e when the home button glows green when your home is ready to arm when your home is armed the home button will glow red when your home is not ready to arm the home button will glow orange why does the menu bar along the bottom of my panel change the menu along the bottom of the screen will change to reflect the status of your home in the left corner there will be a house icon that reflects whether your home is unarmed armed staying or armed leaving in the middle the current temperature of your home will be reflected and in the right corner there is a static menu icon what happens when an alarm is triggered the alarm processes will vary state by state but in general when a fire alarm is triggered we will your st contact number will be called if there is no contact we will dispatch your local fire department after attempting to dispatch all contact numbers will be called in order to notify you of our actions when a medical alarm is triggered we will connect over your panel or— contact you over our vivint live system if available when not available we will attempt your first contact number if there is no contact over the panel or reached at the st contact number we will dispatch a local agency after attempting to dispatch all contact numbers will be called in order to notify you of our actions when a duress alarm is triggered we will connect over your panel or— contact you over our vivint live system listening in for  seconds if no suspicious activity is heard the operator will disconnect from the panel and dispatch the local agency if suspicious activity is heard the operator will stay on the line having another operator dispatch the local agency after attempting to dispatch all contact numbers will be called in order to notify you of our actions when a panic alarm is triggered we will connect over your panel or— contact you over our vivint live system if there is no contact your st contact number will be called if there is no contact your nd contact number will be called note the nd contact number is only called before dispatch if it is also defined as a site number if there is no contact we will dispatch a local agency after attempting to dispatch all contact numbers will be called in order to notify you of our actions when a burglary alarm is triggered we will connect over your panel or— contact you over our vivint live system if there is no contact your st contact number will be called if there is no contact your nd contact number will be called if there is no contact at either number we will dispatch a local agency after attempting to dispatch all contact numbers will be called in order to notify you of our actions can’t find what you were looking for call  get a free quote now by clicking this button you consent for vivint to use automated technology including prerecorded messages and texts to contact you at the number and email provided about vivint offers this consent is not required to make a purchase request quote or call  your information is secure support ceo promise contact us the neighborhood smart resources licenses military families customer stories corporate blog company about us careers newsroom vivint gives back investor relations store locations leadership partners internet solar vivint louisiana support ceo promise contact us the neighborhood smart resources licenses military families customer stories corporate blog company about us careers newsroom vivint gives back investor relations store locations leadership partners internet solar vivint louisiana verify a smart home pro copyright   vivint inc all rights reserved terms of use privacy policy legal product recall customer service support and sales  contact vivint solar closelets get in touchwe’re here to help call or email us with any inquiries we promise to always connect you to a human and never share your personal informationsales if you’re considering solar our sales representatives can answer any of your questions and help you get started if you’re a